*Ubicu* te ako se ne predomisliš! (I will kill you if you don't change your mind!)

*Ubila* ga je ljubomora. (Jealousy killed him.)

*Ubijene* su joj nade. (Her hopes were killed.)

*Ubicom* se bavi policija. (The police is dealing with the killer.)

*Ubicu* nikada neće uhvatiti. (They'll never catch the killer.)

*Ubilo* ga je zločin. (Crime killed him.)

*Ubicama* se sudi u sudu. (Killers are judged in court.)

*Ubila* ga je bijeda. (Misery killed him.)

*Ubicom* je postao. (He became a killer.)

*Ubicama* je plaćeno. (They were paid by the killers.)